# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# combined — __hash__, __eq__, __bool__ across all 14 asyncio subjects
#
# Covers the full matrix: 14 classes x 3 methods = 42 rows.
# __hash__: true only for asyncio.TimerHandle; false for all others.
# __eq__:   true only for asyncio.TimerHandle; false for all others.
# __bool__: false for all 14 classes.
# asyncio.TimerHandle is the single outlier — it defines comparison and hashing
# to support ordered scheduling (min-heap) in the event loop.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

